            "text": "<p>The covers are machine washable, made from regenerative Good Earth Cotton. The inners are filled with soft fluff made from recycled plastic water bottles.</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/BrownBENI.webp"
          }
        },
        "feature_MNUTrW": {
          "type": "feature",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "shopify://shop_images/004-drop.svg",
            "tab_label": "Care guide",
            "subheading": "Care guide",
            "text": "<p>Keeping your BENI BED fluffy is easy. Just like you would with your doona or pillows, it's as simple as giving it a good shake.</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1_73141ba0-e763-4a7c-96ad-8030e5910ef9.webp"
          }
